      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>to a separate pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681838376983-x200.jpg",
