            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened slightly</p><p>Once the sauce has thickened, press down on your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to release the juice – this is your <strong>balsamic tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681838381375-x200.jpg",
