            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> to a plate and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Coat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in the flour, pressing firmly to coat them evenly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
