      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the<strong> coated fish</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
