      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, return the potatoes to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, a splash of<strong> milk </strong>and the<strong> chopped basil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>basil mash</strong></p>",
