    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> golden basa</strong> over the <strong>basil mash</strong> with the <strong>balsamic tomato sauce </strong>drizzled over the top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>basil leaves</strong></p><p>Season with a crack of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
